<br>
“He…Celo…the thing that was Celo…I saw it in the Field of Bone. It was only there briefly, for a second. It transformed into a scaled wolf and ran away. I called to Beneb and Echtelion but by the time they arrived, it had gone.”<br>
<br>
She looked down, looking sad, forlorn and slightly tearful. After a few moments she seemed to compose herself and looked up. She wrinkled her nose.<br>
<br>
“When are they going to do something about that stench? And where is that rancid little dwarf anyway?” <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=evansec>Evansec</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://hometown.aol.com/xxianbamloviexx/images/mercury9510.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I like pie</span><br>  Posts: 146<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/5/04 6:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=832.topic&index=24>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/xxianbamloviexx/images/mercury9510.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Chosen Spirit</span><hr size=1> **knocks lightly on the door**<br>
