<br>
&quot;Help me, Darn it!!!<br>
<br>
Binka runs to Neomiah's side, ready to defend her injured friend...<br>
<br>
&quot;Neo!  Who did this to you?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;That bartender served me some skunked ale....been sitting on the crapper for 6 hours...m'legs are asleep and m'butt is on fire!&quot;<br>
<br>
It takes all of Binka's restraint not to bust out in laughter...<br>
<br>
Neomiah continues, &quot;...Anyone see Toraka?  I need him or another Alchemist to mix me up some ointment.&quot;<br>
<br>
Binka helps Neomiah back to his feet, and her demeanor turns serious. <br>
<br>
&quot;Neo we must go as soon as your ready to help search for Celo.  Viala has sent word that she believes he is somewhere in Kunark.  If we find him we will send word to the rest of Chosen Spirit, that we may overwhelm him in force and subdue him.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Aye m'lady, give me a moment.  I will be ready once I locate m'ointment.&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah goes back to searching through his packs....<br>
<br>
