She then listens to Binka's and Neo's discussion, and nods in agreement.<br>
<br>
Then, after a sudden idea struck her mind, she picks up a big bottle of red wine from the bar, uncorks it and sneaks behind Neo, putting the cork into one of his bags with skilled fingers, making sure he doesnt notice.<br>
<br>
She then goes back to the bar, whistling a little tune.<br>
Muttering to herself, she says 'It might not be ta best way, but it winn definitny be ta fastest', and snickers.<br>
She climbs her chair and keeps her eyes on Neo, eager to see if her evil plan works out...<br>
