<br>
Skilfully she lifted the ointment from Neo’s bag. Behind her back, she deftly unscrewed the top of a bottle she had removed from the table a few moments before. A few drops of “Halas Hotz Extreme Condiment” dribbled over the lip on the bottle and into the ointment. As they hit, there was a faint hiss. Ahh, clearly a vintage year!<br>
<br>
Binka quickly mixed it in with her fingertip and returned the ointment to Neomiah’s bag. She would have to scrub her hands thoroughly after touching it. Even then, it would be inadvisable to put that particular finger near any orifice for at least a week, after coming into contact with the Halas Hotz.<br>
<br>
She settled back, again retrieving popcorn from some hidden part of her armour. The fun had only just started…  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=czakoriah>Czakoriah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 168<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/12/04 2:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=832.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Chosen Spirit</span><hr size=1> &quot;Ah here it is...&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah pulls out the ointment from his packs.<br>
<br>
&quot;Pardon me m'ladies, but I have some personal matters to take care of...&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah limps out the door and toward the outhouse.<br>
<br>
&quot;...........&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;.....YEEEEOOOOWWWW!!!!!!!!!!!!!!&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah bursts through the door of the bar knocking the drinks from a beermaids tray onto an Ogre playing cards as he dashes to his packs.<br>
<br>
