<br>
&quot;Hey backoff Celo!!!  You are gonna kill em!!!&quot;  <br>
<br>
Khlsin looks to Darina who has now begun to cast her own spell...<br>
<br>
&quot;Yesss...He isss about to die!&quot;<br>
<br>
Khlsin finishs weaving his final spell...<br>
<br>
Neomiah arches his back and hands recoil outward as he releases a blood curdling scream.<br>
<br>
Darina's spell lands too late...Neomiah is dead.<br>
<br>
Darina runs upto Neomiah's corpse...and cradles him in her arms...<br>
<br>
&quot;Celo, you bastard!  You killed Neo...&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Yesss...I did&quot;<br>
<br>
Khlsin begins casting another spell...<br>
<br>
Darina jumps to her feet makes ready her weapon and begins casting her own spell....<br>
<br>
Khlsin begins to laugh, and says &quot;The days of discord are coming...you will all die...&quot;<br>
<br>
Darina's spell finishes but to no effect for Khlsin has already faded away...<br>
<br>
